{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>如果二叉树的左右子树的结构是对称的，即两棵子树皆为空，或者皆不空，则称该二叉树是对称的。编程判断给定的二叉树是否对称.<p><p>例：如下图中的二叉树T1是对称的，T2是不对称的。<p><p>![](pic/1368.gif)<p><p>二叉树用顺序结构给出，若读到#则为空，二叉树T1=ABCDE，T2=ABCD#E，如果二叉树是对称的，输出“Yes”,反之输出“No”。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"对称二叉树 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>如果二叉树是对称的，输出“Yes”,反之输出“No”。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>二叉树用顺序结构给出，若读到#则为空。<p>","examples":"<input>ABCDE\n</input><output>Yes\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1368","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}